Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊... 老妈果然是生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是鬼一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是要离家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果被反驳「你做得到的话 请便」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的唇枪舌战么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这个我睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这毛巾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这个我也睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在睡觉上花了多少工夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静下心来好好想想 离家出走非长久之计
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能不去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 你有资格这么说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 安城 学校一旦不去了 会变得很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一天很轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一天没有任何改变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 既然没有改变的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.83,0:00:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日复一日 日积月累
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回过神来 自己已经...真的无所事事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我能自以为了不起说出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:00:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.46,0:01:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海很厉害呢  不是白白在家里呆着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.70,0:01:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然宿海还是一点也没有变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使自己处境一团糟还是只考虑他人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直这样 只考虑别人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这种人 面麻才是一直
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 和雪集也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直被面麻所束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样是不是不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 现在还在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 所以我说 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 没有相信面麻的事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.44,0:01:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也不是说不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:01:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买到了咖喱牛肉 鸣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,520日元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱牛肉 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这 不是那个样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来看日记 呜哇 呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的咖喱牛肉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了这个 就能明白面麻的愿望了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所不了解的面麻存在于此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所不知道的面麻的想法存在于此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（今天和大家一起玩了  好有趣）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（今天和大家一起玩了  好开心）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好敷衍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣和开心 这没有什么区别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不擅长作文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个稍微有点不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和大家一起玩的时候 摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这里也不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和大家去看望仁碳的妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探望么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 大家一直一起去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳的妈妈一直在医院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 给神写信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让仁碳的妈妈早日恢复健康
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家决定一起做烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然觉得很困难 但还是努力做了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把信放入火箭烟花 寄给神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 愿望是不是就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 一定是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候做了 但是却失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 宿海？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不良仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏人仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不在意仁碳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半夜吃东西会变成猪的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成猪的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 盐拉面 鸡蛋汤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健拉面没有买到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你点好吃的转变下你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸差不多要回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 明天我也会去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不要跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是奖励 张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要做奇怪的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 为什么学校放假还穿制服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:08:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系 穿什么样式是自己的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依据火药取缔法烟火火药使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要十八岁以上取得国家资格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是玩具烟火的话还能试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且需要许可证
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然行不通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 一般来说烟火之类也是需要资格的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 说起来 昨天打扫的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集许多烟火将凌乱的火药整理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒入手纸芯里 点燃后失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的 好恐怖 小孩子好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 以前以为这样是可行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 以前认为这么做的话一定能飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:09:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为能比祭典更加绚丽得飞上天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生看起来完全就是个大叔了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉自己什么都能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那个时候觉得自己无所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先摸索可行的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么说 怎么想也是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们再怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这若不是你所说的面麻的愿望的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是徒劳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海君 你有向你身边的面麻确认过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向本人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能畏惧向她本人确认吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬间似曾相识
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直先行一步的宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和看着他的可怜的雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天要不是那家伙说在秘密基地集合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天不是面麻提出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被面麻的电话叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 说是那天有话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易回忆起来 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为宿海在场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘记了重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:11:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻说是要瞒着宿海集合的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 面麻她？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}第七话 真正的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟火 我认识能制作的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 在我工地的大叔是祭典的烟火师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 仁太 想做烟火？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么... 不由得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 波波他们也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那我去拜托他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 仁碳 仁碳 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}走不出空纳鲁的街道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}怎么了？ 我帮你先联络下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...这件事下次再说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最简单的烟火也需要这个数
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十万？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.64,0:12:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我就从来没见过这么多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的 一定还会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会和小鸣拼死打工的 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你别擅作主张好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不很好嘛 互相帮助嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的 小鸣一周七天都打工 很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呀 我还没说我要打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也 打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要将金额输入到这里是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是中古的价格 这里是新品的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 然后将差额输入到这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.07,0:12:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我花一个月才习惯的东西 你就这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太花时间了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这就完全不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 又来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 果然是她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 传言中的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工没请假呢 却旷课了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 看 那小子不是总不来学校的那个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他俩之间绝对有事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 艳福不浅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎...光临！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子傻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干 干嘛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不自觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何只要这样 就感觉和从前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把胶带拿给我下 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 宿..海...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着 小鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个不算的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海在打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放烟花的事情 他好像很认真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？我们也来筹备些钱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要与宿海同流合污吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不想做的话 我更无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 要不出来下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来喝点茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 马上就要考试了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是级部第四
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,级部第二你在说什么呀 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要尾随你已经很累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 竟然这么晚才回来 不良少年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去洗澡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳绝对不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上立刻就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}早晨很早就出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是小汪汪的节目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小汪汪要是母的话 仁碳绝对会对它做一些奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的小汪汪叫奥斯卡鲁 雌性 七岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 沙皮 好可爱 皱皮好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是母的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先来为我们的可爱小嘉宾打声招呼吧 欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请先签名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 仁太不上学了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？没有啊 为何这样问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起啊 问如此奇怪的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 之前有看到他貌似在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这些事 都跟你说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是啊 但我家还是主张自由意识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于他自己的事情 都由他自己做决定 不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 不行的 不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是波波 还没轮到我值班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳的话 店长好像很喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他晚上和你在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？羊山的施工现场？这活是不是太重啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也是哦 想赚多钱的话 体力劳动是首选
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭烟花什么的 钱也就随之而飞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望...面麻的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该更多的考虑一下自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这态度 很让人烦躁的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 雪集有打过电话来？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 偶尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们要是能来就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很在意仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 仁碳就是仁碳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也一直这么叫着嘛 我叫仁碳有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙很拼命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是 很帅的 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻在没有为自己考虑的期间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳却一直都在为面麻考虑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 注意脚下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擅自改变灯光的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风能吹得动灯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真帅啊 闪闪发光的仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了一堆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的肚子是有极限的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:20:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妈妈做的味道好像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个仁碳 在学校很辛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 嗯 但很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎么说呢 感觉比在家里过的轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种活着的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是 我不是说那种实际意义的活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我迄今为止都是那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻啊 只要看到有生存感的仁碳 也就感觉自己也活着一般
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.31,0:20:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我先把定金拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.62,0:20:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以先用这些开始做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊 真不好意思 这事不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对庆典的管理员不小心说漏了嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着他生气的说「你竟然帮高中生」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是如此拼命努力赚钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个管理员是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接去跟他说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是 本间家的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻家的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太君他们好像在努力地为你做各种事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是在开玩笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:22:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我啊 是超和平克星哦
